_header: Alas what planet was I born under
_description: The Vicissitudes of Love — three stanzas rhyme royal.

CULFf16.First Lines:
Alas what planet was y born vndirMy hert ys set thus veray
                    feythfullyThow y be heuy hyt ys no wondirThat in your grace y stand
                    not perfetely…
CULFf16.Last Lines:
…Ther ys in me for wo no certaynteffor lacke of grace thes
                    parties shal yflee
